from typing import List, Union
from accessor import getValue, setValue

audio_1_url = 'https://public-static-files.superannotate.com/documentation/audio/audio_track_1.mp3'
audio_2_url = 'https://public-static-files.superannotate.com/documentation/audio/audio_track_2.mp3'

toggle = 1

def on_change_audio_click(path: List[Union[str, int]]):
    global toggle
    if (toggle == 1):
        setValue(['audio'], audio_2_url)
        toggle = 2
    elif (toggle == 2):
        setValue(['audio'], audio_1_url)
        toggle = 1

    return
